archer - Prop Trading Firm - 𝑪𝒉𝒊𝒄𝒂𝒈𝒐 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐬 📈 Quant Trader - Crypto Trading Firm 📈 Crypto Quant Trader - Systematic Hedge Fund 📈 Options Quant Trader - Prop Trading Firm - 𝒇𝒖𝒍𝒍𝒚 𝒓𝒆𝒎𝒐𝒕𝒆 To find out more about any of these positions, or for a general chat on the market, don''t hesitate to reach out! Emily Lockyer emily@durlstonpartners.com hashtag#careers hashtag#softwareengineers hashtag#quantresearchers hashtag#traders hashtag#devops …more', '10mo • 10 months ago • Visible to anyone on or off LinkedIn', 8, 0, 0, 'image', 0, NULL);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO posts (company_key, author_kind, author_name, author_url, post_url, post_text, posted_date, reactions_count, comments_count, reposts_count, media_type, is_repost, original_author) VALUES ('durlston-partners', 'company', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/durlston-partners/posts', 'https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7341443012721278977/', 'The UAE Hedge Fund space is growing at a phenomenal rate. Having been on the ground for 18 months and advising clients on their move to Dubai and Abu Dhabi, we are not only seeing a huge influx of talent from London but also Singapore, Hong Kong and even New York. The recent conflict hasn''t deterred the upward trend, as covered by Bloomberg''s Hema Parmar featuring our very own Rahnpreet Sandhu, link in the comments section. For real time up to date market information please reach out to our team in Dubai and Abud Dhabi, Warwick Poelman (واريك بولمان) Rahnpreet Sandhu Vikram Tandon Joshwa Shah James Skelt Jared Wolfaardt …more', '10mo • 10 months ago • Visible to anyone on or off LinkedIn', 16, 1, 2, 'image', 0, NULL);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO posts (company_key, author_kind, author_name, author_url, post_url, post_text, posted_date, reactions_count, comments_count, reposts_count, media_type, is_repost, original_author) VALUES ('durlston-partners', 'company', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/durlston-partners/posts', 'https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7341415710960545793/', '𝐑𝐞𝐦𝐨𝐭𝐞 𝐑𝐨𝐥𝐞𝐬 - 𝐅𝐫𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐝/𝐏𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐧/𝐂++ - 𝐔𝐩 𝐭𝐨 $𝟔𝟎𝟎𝐤 𝐓𝐂 - Durlston Partners 🎯Middle Office Developer - HFT - Python - (needs strong finance background) - Up to $350k TC - Develop end-to-end systems processing millions of transactions across multiple exchanges. 🎯Core Developer - HFT - C++ - Up to £300k TC - build scalable and reliable core trading infrastructure from scratch, with excellent system architecture and design skills. 🎯Strategy Developer - HFT - C++ - up to $600k TC+ - Advanced HFT/C++ Optimisation skills working directly on trading strategies improving performance. 🎯Frontend Developer - FinTech Start up - React/React Native - Up to £130k+ Equity (not Options), build out a new Mobile App and Web based interface for a highly successful FinTech platform. If you would like further information on any of the above, please get in touch. james@durlstonpartners.com Even if you aren''t actively looking and you want to learn more about the market/what roles are active currently, I would be happy to have a discreet chat. hashtag#hft hashtag#frontend hashtag#cplusplus hashtag#python hashtag#middleoffice hashtag#softwaredevelopment hashtag#softwareengineering hashtag#highfrequencytrading hashtag#fintech hashtag#remotejobs …more', '10mo • 10 months ago • Visible to anyone on or off LinkedIn', 10, 1, 0, 'image', 0, NULL);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO posts (company_key, author_kind, author_name, author_url, post_url, post_text, posted_date, reactions_count, comments_count, reposts_count, media_type, is_repost, original_author) VALUES ('durlston-partners', 'company', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/durlston-partners/posts', 'https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7341038218265436160/', '𝐅𝐫𝐞𝐞 𝐂𝐨𝐟𝐟𝐞𝐞 𝐂𝐥𝐮𝐛!! Calling Buy Side/Sell Side Developers & QDs & Quants - Let me know if you would like to grab a hashtag#coffee on me close to your office, so I can give you a clear and accurate overview of the current market. Durlston Partners have been working in the industry for over 12 years, having built relationships with the leading hashtag#HighFrequencyTrading firms and hashtag#hedgefunds as well as some of the most impressive start-ups run by industry titans. If you would like to have an initial discreet chat over the phone or meet for a coffee and get an insight into roles, comp packages and market news - reach out to me below. I''m out and about in the hashtag#WestEnd, hashtag#City hashtag#CanaryWharf :) ✉️ louis@durlstonpartners.com Louis Esquerré-Gow …more', '10mo • 10 months ago • Visible to anyone on or off LinkedIn', 6, 0, 0, 'image', 0, NULL);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO posts (company_key, author_kind, author_name, author_url, post_url, post_text, posted_date, reactions_count, comments_count, reposts_count, media_type, is_repost, original_author) VALUES ('durlston-partners', 'company', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/durlston-partners/posts', 'https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7340656993835081729/', '𝗙𝗼𝗿𝗲𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗻𝘁 𝗼𝗳 𝗔𝗜/𝗟𝗟𝗠𝘀 𝗶𝗻 𝗤𝘂𝗮𝗻𝘁 𝗧𝗿𝗮𝗱𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘄𝗶𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗨𝗔𝗘 Please message me if you''re keen to get an understanding of the region, the opportunities for you, and what relocation looks like in practical terms. 📥 Rahnpreet Sandhu …more', '10mo • 10 months ago • Visible to anyone on or off LinkedIn', 9, 0, 1, 'image', 0, NULL);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO posts (company_key, author_kind, author_name, author_url, post_url, post_text, posted_date, reactions_count, comments_count, reposts_count, media_type, is_repost, original_author) VALUES ('durlston-partners', 'company', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/durlston-partners/posts', 'https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7340653189966299136/', 'Another great tech meetup in Dubai last Friday, organised by our very own Joshwa Shah. We''re growing a community of Software Engineers from hedge funds, HFT, crypto (CeFi and DeFi) and AI/ML in Dubai.. whether you''re new to the region or have been here for years, it’s a great way to connect, swap ideas, and expand your network in a relaxed setting. We’ve been running these meetups monthly, but things will slow down a bit over the summer. The next one will likely be in September, and we’re already excited to bring the community back together then. If you''d like to be kept in the loop about future events, drop a line to: events@durlstonpartners.com to register your interest. hashtag#TechCommunity hashtag#DubaiEvents hashtag#Quant hashtag#FinTech hashtag#Networking hashtag#DurlstonPartners hashtag#Meetup hashtag#Events …more', '10mo • 10 months ago • Visible to anyone on or off LinkedIn', 12, 0, 0, 'image', 0, NULL);
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO posts (company_key, author_kind, author_name, author_url, post_url, post_text, posted_date, reactions_count, comments_count, reposts_count, media_type, is_repost, original_author) VALUES ('durlston-partners', 'company', NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/durlston-partners/posts', 'https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7340317222575173632/', 'What if you could work on the fastest trading systems in the world… without ever setting foot in an office? A world-class High-Frequency Trading firm is hiring. They’re not looking for "just another developer”. They’re after engineers who live and breathe performance People who obsess over nanoseconds, optimise down to the metal, and get a thrill from beating the benchmark. And here’s the kicker: 📍 You can work from anywhere in Europe 💥 Build latency-critical systems in modern C++ (17/20) 💼 No meetings for the sake of it. No layers of management. Just elite engineering, done right. 💰 Compensation? Let’s just say it’s designed to attract the best in the world. If you’ve built low-latency, high-throughput systems, whether in trading, gaming, networking or any real-time environment, this is one of the few roles that will actually challenge you. Daniel Frugtniet Hagen …more', '10mo • 10 months ago • Visible to anyone on or off LinkedIn', 6, 1, 0, 'image', 0, NULL);
